            <div class="content">
                <div class="celebration-header">🎂🎈🎉</div>
                
                <div class="celebration-box">
                    <div class="celebration-title">🌟 Birthday Celebration Time! 🌟</div>
                    
                    <div class="message-content">
                        Hi <strong><t t-out="object.company_id.name or 'OSUS Properties'"/></strong> Family,<br/><br/>
                        
                        Today is <span class="birthday-name-highlight"><t t-out="object.name or ''"/></span>'s special day! 🎉<br/><br/>
                        
                        Let's come together to make this birthday memorable by sending warm wishes 
                        and celebrating our amazing colleague from the <strong>OSUS Properties family</strong>.<br/><br/>
                        
