                            💫 "Birthdays are nature's way of telling us to eat more cake and spread more joy!" 🍰
                        </div>
                        
                        Please take a moment to send your birthday greetings and make 
                        <strong><t t-out="object.name or ''"/></strong>'s day extra special!<br/><br/>
                        
                        <a href="https://t.me/+bWdZc6_TZME5ODM0" target="_blank" class="cta-button">
                            🎁 Send OSUS Birthday Wishes 🎁
                        </a><br/><br/>
                        
                        <div class="company-signature">
                            Kind Regards,<br/>
                            <strong>The <t t-out="object.company_id.name or 'OSUS Properties'"/> Team</strong>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- OSUS Properties Footer -->
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-company"><t t-out="object.company_id.name or 'OSUS Properties'"/></div>
